      <h2>School Transport</h2>
      <p>The school has a fleet of many buses at its own disposal. The buses pick up the students from their stoppage from different areas of the city and near by areas and drop them at the scheduled stoppage. Each bus driver has been provided with a cell phone for the convenience of contacting the driver at any points in case of urgency. All the students using the school buses are expected to be on the left side of their bus stop at least ten minutes prior to the arrival time of the bus. The buses will not wait for the late comers The children should stay away from the main road until the bus arrives. No student should come near the entry door of the bus until it has made a complete halt. All the students must occupy vacant seats immediately after boarding in buses. No student is allowed to eat anything inside the bus. The driverï¿½s attention must not be distracted for any reason whatsoever it is. Bus facility cannot be withdrawn in mid session of the academic calendar.
